name: Gen 4 - Buck Teeth (VERY RARE)
bio: Sup playa! My name's Gen 4 - Buck Teeth (VERY RARE). I once peed on Marie Antoinette's cat. They had it coming. When my owner isn't watching, I steal their oversized sweaters and use them for litter paper. I'm not sorry. I look forward to slappin' da bass with you.
